                單元 4．Resonant Modes, Bilinear Transformation between Impedance and Reflection Coefficient 
                





 




 
                單元 5．Single-stub and Double-stub Impedance Transformers 
                





 




 
                單元 6．Lossy Line and Diffusion Equation 
                





 




 
                單元 7．Potential Functions and Hertzian Dipole 
                





 




 
